### 8. MODIFY: `apps/web/src/routes/_chat.settings.tsx`

Four changes:

1. **Remove** the `THEME_OPTIONS` const (lines 25–41)
2. **Remove** `import { useTheme } from "../hooks/useTheme"` (it will be unused after step 3)
3. **Remove** `const { theme, setTheme, resolvedTheme } = useTheme();` from `SettingsRouteView` (line 90)
4. **Add** `import { ThemeSelector } from "../components/ThemeSelector";`
5. **Replace** the entire Appearance `<section>` body (lines 202–243) with:

```tsx
<section className="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-5">
  <div className="mb-4">
    <h2 className="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Appearance</h2>
    <p className="mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
      Choose how T3 Code handles light and dark mode.
    </p>
  </div>
  <ThemeSelector />
